Mwani Finance Hub
Project Overview
Mwani Finance Hub is a digital platform designed to help farmer’s access fair market prices and connect directly with government-approved buyers, reducing exploitation by middlemen.

 Objectives
•	Provide transparent agricultural market pricing
•	Connect farmers with official buyers
•	Improve income stability for farmers

